OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy and dry through
OL,6,FTuesday morning, some brighter spells
OL,7,Flikely especially in east. Slow-moving
OL,8,Fshowers look set to arrive and turn
OL,9,Frather heavy late afternoon and into
OL,10,Fthe evening. Turning dry overnight
OL,11,Fwith winds continuing light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers fading during Tuesday
OL,14,Fevening then a fine night with some
OL,15,Fcloud breaks, allowing temperatures to
OL,16,Fdip. Winds remaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
