OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FWednesday morning generally
OL,6,Fdry and bright. Thickening cloud in
OL,7,Fthe afternoon brings a risk of rain
OL,8,Flater in the afternoon. Most parts
OL,9,Fseeing rain by evening. Rain clearing
OL,10,Fovernight, breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FThursday, Friday and Saturday are
OL,14,Flikely to remain mostly dry and
OL,15,Fbreezy, with some clear or sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Temperatures close or a little
OL,17,Fabove average throughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
